General.Name: Bong AB (publ)
General.Description: Bong AB (publ) manufactures and sells specialty packaging and envelope products. It provides solutions for distribution and packaging of information, advertising materials, and lightweight goods. The company offers envelopes, carrier bags for the retail trade, and packaging products for e-commerce. It also provides light packaging products; and solutions for distribution and packaging of information, advertising materials, and lightweight goods. The company has operations in Germany, Poland, Benelux, Romania, Switzerland, Czech Republic, France, Italy, Spain, Sweden, Norway, Denmark, Baltics, Morocco, Ireland, Europe, Finland, the United Kingdom, and Tunisia. Bong AB (publ) was founded in 1737 and is headquartered in Kristianstad, Sweden.
